{"tid":448243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國戰機撞鳥墜毀 小鳥竟還好端端活著...","createTime":"2017-10-26T04:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T13:46:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":95,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"b3321e510b31cce01ee39223b06ae16735f91add","tid":448243,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/124120_674ff566cef24c915593a0d838a3fea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F124120_674ff566cef24c915593a0d838a3fea7.jpg&h=f4c04ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國一架戰機疑似遭鳥撞擊墜毀，影片在網路上瘋傳，因為戰機墜毀時即爆炸，大火燃燒飛機，有人在戰機殘骸上發現一隻受傷的鳥，這隻小鳥竟然沒死，讓現場眾人直呼：「太牛了唄！」<br />\n<br />\n中國教練-9戰機昨在北方墜毀，因爆炸聲和火光吸引不少民眾圍觀，有民眾拿起手機錄影，並將影片傳到網路上。戰機雖然墜毀，但機上兩名飛行員跳傘成功保住性命，並無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n教練-9戰機疑似是被鳥撞機才會墜毀，民眾在飛機殘骸上發現有隻受傷的小鳥，被民眾撿到時，牠還在動，讓現場的人嘖嘖稱奇。不過究竟這隻鳥是否就是撞擊戰機的鳥，還尚未確定，目前仍在調查當中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2233811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2233811&d=FHh3riwQIUFzR5hGpMP2s5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=054a769b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2233811&h=c9657756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2233811</a>"},{"pid":"00483fa49641aeb15ddc35b27e8c766b07959845","tid":448243,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"操作員問題"},{"pid":"722dc50b8b4d2e5b57c459d866b13ffa025260c6","tid":448243,"uid":37957,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"中國真係和平的獅子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f918b49b9f16e5d5afe7e9b1c2626f8b586e6a3","tid":448243,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:00:07.000Z